Gary W. McGann

Age : 66Public asset : 14,012,496 USDLinked companies :  Paddy Power Betfair PLC -  ARYZTA AG -  Green Reit PLC -  Carton de Colombia S.A. 





Summary 



Mr. Gary W. McGann is Chairman at Aryzta AG, Non-Executive Chairman at Paddy Power Betfair Plc, Chairman at Aon Ireland Ltd. and Chairman at Sicon Ltd.He is on the Board of Directors at Green REIT Plc, Aon MacDonagh & Boland Group Ltd., Carton de Colombia SA, Irish Business & Employers Confederation and UCD Michael Smurfit Graduate School of Business. Mr. McGann was previously employed as Chairman by Paddy Power Plc, Chairman by Confederation of European Paper Industries, Non-Executive Director by UDG Healthcare Plc, Non-Executive Director by Smurfit Kappa Group Plc, Chief Executive Officer by Jefferson Smurfit Group Ltd., Chief Executive Officer by Aer Lingus Ltd., Chairman by Dublin Airport Authority Plc, a Member by European Round Table of Industrialists, Chief Executive Officer by Gilbey's of Ireland, Chief Executive Officer by Grand Metropolitan Finance Plc, and an Independent Director by Multi Packaging Solutions International Ltd.He also served on the board at Anglo Irish Bank Corp. Ltd. and Smurfit Kappa Acquisitions Unlimited Co.



