Notes to Editors:
About the European Pulp and Paper Outlook Conference (www.risi.com/euroconf)
The Sixteenth RISI European Pulp and Paper Outlook Conference will be held at the Marriott Prague Hotel in the Czech Republic on March 10-12, 2014. The conference will address some of the key issues facing the European pulp and paper industry. More information regarding the conference program and registration details can be found at www.risi.com/euroconf.
About Smurfit Kappa (www.smurfitkappa.com)
Smurfit Kappa is one of the leading producers of paper-based packaging in the world, with around 41,000 employees in approximately 350 production sites across 32 countries and with a sales revenue of Euro 7.3 billion ($9.2 billion) in 2012.
Smurfit Kappa headquarters are in Dublin with regional headquarters in Paris (Europe) and Miami (the Americas).
About RISI (www.risi.com)
RISI is the leading information provider for the global forest products industry. The company works with clients in the pulp and paper, wood products, timber, biomass, tissue, nonwovens, printing and publishing industries to help them make better decisions.
Headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts, RISI operates additional offices throughout North and South America, Europe and Asia.









